Documentation.Data: Addressbook of an organization. Contains either members (users) of an organization, having refUserBusinessPartnerId filled or customers of an organization (others). An employee can have two records in this table - as a user and optionally as an internal customer.
Reference to user account table. Mandatory for members of an organization.
Ke které společnosti daný kontakt patří. Společnost je kontakt z adresáře.
